# Lingmo OS System Libraries
#
# This directory contains core system shared libraries.
# These libraries are essential for basic system operation.
#
# LD_LIBRARY_PATH: /system/lib has highest priority
#
# Contents:
#   - C runtime (libc, libm, etc.)
#   - Core system libraries (libpthread, libdl)
#   - Essential dynamic linker support
#
# Architecture: @ARCH@
# @DISTRO_NAME@ @VERSION@
# Build: @BUILD_VER@
